

#### Java - Spring Boot REST Controller
```
You are a world-class software engineer. Generate a complete Spring Boot REST controller boilerplate:
- Entity: [ENTITY_NAME]
- Base URL: /api/[ENTITY_PLURAL]
- Operations: CRUD + custom operations

Include:
- @RestController and @RequestMapping annotations
- All standard CRUD endpoints (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
- Request/Response DTOs
- Input validation with @Valid
- Exception handling with @ControllerAdvice
- Swagger/OpenAPI documentation
- Security annotations
- Pagination support for list operations
- Audit logging
```
